## MPC Objective Function

```markdown
# Model Predictive Control

The finite-horizon optimization problem is:

$$
\min_{u_{0:N-1}}
\sum_{k=0}^{N-1}
\left(
 e_k^T Q e_k
+
u_k^T R u_k
\right)
+
e_N^T P e_N
$$
```

---

## MPC Constraints

```markdown
# MPC Constraints

subject to:

$$
x_{k+1}
=
f(x_k,u_k)
$$

$$
u_k
\in
\mathcal U
$$

$$
x_k
\in
\mathcal X
$$
```

