# 9. RRT* Path Planning

## Suggested File

```text
docs/theory/path_planning.md
```

---

## Random Sampling

```markdown
# Random Sampling

$$
x_{rand}
\sim
\mathrm{Uniform}(\chi)
$$
```

---

## Nearest Node Search

```markdown
# Nearest Node Search

$$
x_{near}
=
\arg\min_{x\in V}
\|x-x_{rand}\|
$$
```

---

## Node Expansion

```markdown
# Node Expansion

$$
d
=
\|x_{rand}-x_{near}\|
$$

$$
x_{new}
=
\begin{cases}
x_{rand}, & d<\eta \\

x_{near}
+
\frac{x_{rand}-x_{near}}{d}\eta,
& \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
$$
```

---

## Search Radius

```markdown
# Search Radius

$$
r
=
\gamma
\left(
\frac{\log |V|}{|V|}
\right)^{1/d}
$$
```

---

## Parent Selection

```markdown
# Parent Selection

$$
x_{min}
=
\arg\min_{x\in X_{near}}
\left(
\mathrm{Cost}(x)
+
\|x-x_{new}\|
\right)
$$
```

---

## Path Cost

```markdown
# Path Cost

$$
\mathrm{Cost}(x)
=
\sum_{i=1}^{n}
\|x_i-x_{i-1}\|
$$
```

---

## Rewiring Condition

```markdown
# Rewiring Condition

$$
\mathrm{Cost}(x_{new})
+
\|x_{new}-x\|
<
\mathrm{Cost}(x)
$$
```

---

## Collision-Free Constraint

```markdown
# Collision-Free Constraint

$$
\mathrm{ObstacleFree}(x_i,x_j)
=
\mathrm{True}
$$
```

