## Projection Interval

```markdown
# Projection Interval

The projection interval is:

$$
\mathrm{Projection}_i
=
[C_i \cdot L-r_i,
C_i \cdot L+r_i]
$$
```

---

## Projection Radius

```markdown
# Projection Radius

$$
r_i
=
 h_{x_i}|u_i\cdot L|
+
h_{y_i}|v_i\cdot L|
+
h_{z_i}|w_i\cdot L|
$$
```

---

## SAT Non-Intersection Condition

```markdown
# SAT Non-Intersection Condition

Two OBBs do not intersect if:

$$
C_i\cdot L+r_i
<
C_j\cdot L-r_j
$$

or:

$$
C_j\cdot L+r_j
<
C_i\cdot L-r_i
$$
```

